OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAnother very
OL,6,Fwarm night for many. Evening showers
OL,7,Fand thunderstorms will ease and
OL,8,Fgradually clear eastwards, leaving a
OL,9,Fdrier and clearer remainder of the
OL,10,Fnight, although western parts may
OL,11,Fperhaps stay cloudier.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FWhile still very warm,
OL,14,Ftemperatures will be a little lower
OL,15,Fthan on previous days. Further periods
OL,16,Fof sunshine will develop, perhaps hazy
OL,17,Fand eventually sparking scattered
OL,18,Fshowers or thunderstorms later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
